name: Natalia Flynn
description: First of all, I am looking for "Mr Right, Honest and Handsome". Character is more important than looks. A perfect spouse is one that is funny and caring. He must be sweet, loving, loyal, and have many other qualities. I would want my man to share his thoughts with me. I want to hear his dreams and to share in his struggles. On the other hand, I will also need someone who will be ready to listen to me, and interested to know what is happening in my life.
